high_descs: Turn left and walk to the counter to the left of the stove.
Pick up the knife behind the glass vase on the counter.
Walk to the pan on the stove.
Place the knife in the pan on the stove.
Pick up the pan on the stove.
Turn around and walk to the sink.
Place the pan in the sink.
anns.task_desc: Place a pan with a knife in it into the sink.

high_descs: Turn to the left, head to the stove
Take the knife from the counter
Take a couple steps to the right, face the stove
Put the knife on the plate on the stove
take the plate with knife
Turn around, head to the sink
put the plate with knife in the sink
anns.task_desc: Take the knife and plate, put them in the sink

high_descs: Turn left into the kitchen and then turn to your left to face the kitchen counter on the left of the stove
Pick up a knife off of the kitchen counter
Move a step to your right and face the stove
Drop the knife in to the frying pan
Pick up the frying pan with the knife in it
Turn right around and face the sink
Drop the frying pan in to the sink
anns.task_desc: Drop a frying pan with a knife in it into the sink
